io.netty.util.collection

Interface IntObjectMap<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type stored in the map.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntObjectHashMap

    public interface IntObjectMap<V>
    Interface for a primitive map that uses ints as keys.
